	   <tr><td colspan=2>Since when has it been "Spirit of THE Wolf"?  It's Spirit of Wolf, no "the".  Hence, SoW.<br><br>And the Lay Hands ability has been around since D&D, where it was called Lay on Hands.  A lot of EQ players played D&D back in the day, so the abbreviation LoH stuck.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
