	   <tr><td colspan=2>Oh and as for weapons...<br><br>At 10 I think I was using a Minotaur axe which is one of the best that can be had at this stage for the money.  You can get one in East commons for 5p.  Or you can hunt minos in Steamfont for them.  They are about 8dmg / 36 dly or so, hitting for around 18.  If you have about 50p to spend you can pick up something a little nicer in East Commons.  However, at this stage when you upgrade make sure it's signficant.  I wouldn't recommend spending your hard earned money on a weapon that is the same dmg/dly as your current but happens to be magic, for instance.  Be patient and save your money for a weapon that will really improve your game.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
