	   <tr><td colspan=2>I usually bash first and then stun to try and conserve mana.  It's pretty rare that anything will get through that, but if neither works the only spell that will give you the chance to cast a second stun is CH.  This incidentally is the only spell I'm concerned with going through, since I can outdamage most other heals against low blues.<br>&nbsp;<br><b>Praetor</b>, 60th Crusader<br>Avatars of Discord</td></tr>
